    <title>Hexo melody 主题配置</title>
    <link href="https://hexo.tangxs0808.ltd/2020/12/10/Hexo-melody-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/"/>
    <id>https://hexo.tangxs0808.ltd/2020/12/10/Hexo-melody-%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</id>
    <published>2020-12-10T02:52:47.000Z</published>
    <updated>2020-12-10T05:04:42.068Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Hexo melody 主题配置<br>基础配置</p><a id="more"></a><h2 id="配置文件"><a href="#配置文件" class="headerlink" title="配置文件"></a>配置文件</h2><p>· 配置文件_config.yml</p><p>· language:  //设置语言</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">default(en)</span><br><span class="line">zh-Hans</span><br><span class="line">en</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="自定义主题色"><a href="#自定义主题色" class="headerlink" title="自定义主题色"></a>自定义主题色</h2><p>TIP</p><p>版本 v1.5.6</p><p>现在你可以修改大部分主题用到的颜色，改成你所喜欢的任何颜色。</p><p>配置melody.yml，比如：</p><p>颜色值必须被双引号包裹，就像”#000”而不是#000。否则将会报错！</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1  theme_color:</span><br><span class="line">2  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span> </span><br><span class="line">3  main: <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">4  paginator: <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">5  button_hover: <span class="string">&quot;#49B1F5&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">6  text_selection: <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">7  link_color: <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">8  hr_color: <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">9  meta_color: <span class="string">&quot;#000&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="代码高亮"><a href="#代码高亮" class="headerlink" title="代码高亮"></a>代码高亮</h2><p>theme-melody 支持了Material Theme全部5种代码高亮样式：</p><p>default<br>darker<br>pale night<br>light<br>ocean (从v1.5.5开始支持)<br>配置主题config</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">highlight_theme: default <span class="comment"># default/darker/pale night/light</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="支持代码复制"><a href="#支持代码复制" class="headerlink" title="支持代码复制"></a>支持代码复制</h3><h2 id="导航菜单"><a href="#导航菜单" class="headerlink" title="导航菜单"></a>导航菜单</h2><p>在右上角的区域是导航菜单项。Hexo有默认的/和/archives的路径。如果你想拥有其他比如tags和categories的页面，请按照下面步骤来操作：</p><p>前往你的Hexo博客的根目录<br>输入hexo new page tags<br>你会找到source/tags/index.md这个文件<br>修改这个文件：</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 ---</span><br><span class="line">2 title: 标签</span><br><span class="line">3 date: 2018-01-05 00:00:00</span><br><span class="line">4 <span class="built_in">type</span>: <span class="string">&quot;tags&quot;</span></span><br><span class="line">5 ---</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>type必须是tags！如果你要增加categories页面的话也是一样的。</p><p>然后配置主题config </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 menu: </span><br><span class="line">2 Home: /</span><br><span class="line">3 Archives: /archives</span><br><span class="line">4 Tags: /tags</span><br><span class="line">5 Categories: /categories</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="meun、Home、等可以自行修改"><a href="#meun、Home、等可以自行修改" class="headerlink" title="meun、Home、等可以自行修改"></a>meun、Home、等可以自行修改</h3><h2 id="文章版权"><a href="#文章版权" class="headerlink" title="文章版权"></a>文章版权</h2><p>TIP</p><p>版本 v1.1</p><p>为你的博客文章展示文章版权和许可协议。</p><p>配置主题config</p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">1 post_copyright:</span><br><span class="line">2  <span class="built_in">enable</span>: <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">3  license: CC BY-NC-SA 3.0 <span class="comment"># 协议名称</span></span><br><span class="line">4  license_url: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/ <span class="comment"># 协议说明地址</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="文章相关二维码"><a href="#文章相关二维码" class="headerlink" title="文章相关二维码"></a>文章相关二维码</h2><p>在你每篇文章的结尾，给读者展示你自己的二维码。二维码的图片url以及相关说明都取决于你。配置格式如下：<br>配置主题config </p><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">QR_code:</span><br><span class="line">1   itemlist:</span><br><span class="line">2   img: https://xxxx1.jpg</span><br><span class="line">3   text: 支付宝打赏</span><br><span class="line">4   itemlist:</span><br><span class="line">5   img: https://xxxx2.jpg</span><br><span class="line">6   text: 微信打赏</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
    
